(5, 'Wade Brantley', 'CEO, ScienceSoft USA', '1612855068.png', 'Joined our team in 2015, Mr. Brantley holds a BSc in Business Management from the University of South Carolina. He brought in nearly 20 years of management experience in technology and finance.', '2021-02-16 23:18:20', '2021-02-09 02:17:48', '2021-02-16 23:18:20'),
