(13, 'ALM with TFS', 'Brainvire provides administrative and management solutions for app dev...', 'Brainvire offers support, coupled with robust solutions for ALM (application lifecycle management).', '<!DOCTYPE html>\r\n<html>\r\n        <head>\r\n            <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\r\n            <link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"https://pro.fontawesome.com/releases/v5.10.0/css/all.css\" integrity=\"sha384-AYmEC3Yw5cVb3ZcuHtOA93w35dYTsvhLPVnYs9eStHfGJvOvKxVfELGroGkvsg+p\" crossorigin=\"anonymous\"/>\r\n            <link href=\"https://unpkg.com/tailwindcss@^2/dist/tailwind.min.css\" rel=\"stylesheet\">\r\n        </head>\r\n    <body>\r\n        <div class=\"block w-full p-6 lg:p-20\">\r\n            <div class=\"w-full md:w-11/12 mx-auto my-9\">\r\n                <h1 class=\"text-2xl md:text-2xl lg:text-4xl text-center mb-16 font-bold text-gray-800\">\r\n                    Benefits of Tier 1 Help Desk for Employees and Clients\r\n                </h1>\r\n            </div>\r\n            <div class=\"border-b-2 border-gray-300 mb-9 pb-9\">\r\n                <img src=\"https://www.scnsoft.com/fleet-management/serge--pukhaev-2.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"w-24 mx-auto mb-6\">\r\n                <a href=\"#\"><h1 class=\"text-2xl md:text-2xl text-blue-600 text-center mb-2\">Veranika Karilova</h1></a>\r\n                <p class=\"text-md text-gray-600 text-center\">\r\n                    Help Desk Manager, ScienceSoft\r\n                </p>\r\n            </div>\r\n            <div class=\"w-full mb-9\" style=\"display: flex; justify-content: space-between; flex-wrap: wrap;\">\r\n                <a href=\"#\" class=\"text-blue-600 text-lg w-full md:w-1/2 uppercase mb-4\">crm</a>\r\n                <div class=\"flex flex-col md:flex-row\">\r\n                    <p class=\"text-md text-gray-600 mb-4 mr-4\">Published:Feb, 2, 2021</p>\r\n                    <div class=\"flex\">\r\n                        <div><i class=\"fal fa-clock mr-4\"></i></div>\r\n                        <div><p class=\"text-md text-gray-600 mb-4\">3 min read</p></div>\r\n                    </div>\r\n                </div>\r\n            </div>\r\n            <div class=\"lg:flex\">\r\n                <div class=\"lg:w-4/12  lg:hidden\">\r\n                    <h1 class=\"text-2xl md:text-2xl mb-6 font-bold text-gray-800\">\r\n                        Table of contents\r\n                    </h1>\r\n                    <hr class=\"w-12 mb-6 border-b-2 border-yellow-300\">\r\n                    <ul style=\"list-style: square;\" class=\"text-blue-700 m-6\">\r\n                        <a href=\"#\"><li class=\"text-md md:text-lg text-blue-600\">Skills needed for tier 1 help desk agents</li>                        </a>\r\n                        <a href=\"#\"><li class=\"text-md md:text-lg text-blue-600\">Benefits of outsourcing tier 1 help desk</li></a>\r\n                    </ul>\r\n                </div>\r\n                <div class=\"w-full lg:w-8/12 mb-9\">\r\n                    <div class=\"my-6\">\r\n                        <img src=\"https://www.scnsoft.com/blog-pictures/crm-pics/tier-1-help-desk-outsourcing.png\" alt=\"\">\r\n                    </div>\r\n                    <p class=\"text-md md:text-xl text-gray-600 mb-6\">\r\n                        There are two major types of tier 1 help desk. <strong>Internal tier 1 \r\n                        help desk</strong> deals with simple issues concerning employees’ work \r\n                        (e.g., password resets), contributing to the improvement of work \r\n                        efficiency. <strong>External, or customer-facing, tier 1 help desk,</strong> manages \r\n                        incoming customer questions and inquiries concerning your products \r\n                        or services. If the resolution of an incoming issue does not require \r\n                        deep technical expertise (e.g., basic product usage instructions, \r\n                        frequently asked questions about a product or service), the issue is \r\n                        fixed right at this level. In case a deeper technical involvement is needed \r\n                        to resolve the issue, it is escalated to the next help desk level. \r\n                        The quality of help desk support your customers receive is as important \r\n                        for them as the quality of products they buy. \r\n                        <a href=\"#\" class=\"text-blue-500 underline\">85% of the customers</a> are \r\n                        ready to spend more on your products if they receive high-quality help desk support.\r\n                    </p>\r\n                    <h1 class=\"text-2xl md:text-2xl mb-6 font-bold text-gray-800\">\r\n                        Skills tier 1 help desk agents need to possess\r\n                    </h1>\r\n                    <p class=\"text-md md:text-xl text-gray-600 mb-6\">\r\n                        Tier 1 help desk specialists deal with basic issues that your employees \r\n                        or customers face. Thus, agents need to have a general understanding of \r\n                        the product or service without the technical expertise needed to resolve complex issues.\r\n                    </p>\r\n                    <p class=\"text-md md:text-xl text-gray-600 mb-6\">\r\n                        The most typical issues that tier 1 help desk specialists work with include:\r\n                        <ul style=\"list-style: circle;\" class=\"text-gray-600 m-6\">\r\n                            <li class=\"text-md md:text-lg\">Password reset.</li>\r\n                            <li class=\"text-md md:text-lg\">Account lock/unlock.</li>\r\n                            <li class=\"text-md md:text-lg\">Providing information on your product/service benefits.</li>\r\n                            <li class=\"text-md md:text-lg\">Product/service availability.</li>\r\n                            <li class=\"text-md md:text-lg\">Payment and shipment issues, etc.</li>\r\n                        </ul>\r\n                    </p>\r\n                    <p class=\"text-md md:text-xl text-gray-600 mb-6\">\r\n                        Both internal and customer-facing tier 1 help desk agents greatly \r\n                        contribute to your company’s image, so they need to possess excellent \r\n                        problem-solving and communication skills.<br><br>\r\n                        For agents to successfully deal with common employee or customer issues, \r\n                        your help desk managers should create detailed scripts for them to follow \r\n                        step-by-step. If your agents cannot resolve the issue, they should be able \r\n                        to escalate it to tier 2 specialists smoothly.\r\n                    </p>\r\n                    <div class=\"card w-full mb-6 p-4 border md:flex\" style=\"align-items: center; justify-content: space-between;\">\r\n                        <div class=\"text\">\r\n                            <h1 class=\"text-2xl md:text-2xl mb-4 font-bold text-gray-800\">\r\n                                Outsource Tier 1 Help Desk\r\n                            </h1>\r\n                            <hr class=\"w-12 mb-4 border-b-2 border-yellow-300 border\">\r\n                            <p class=\"text-md md:text-lg text-gray-600 mb-4\">\r\n                                ScienceSoft’s team is ready to take over your tier 1 help \r\n                                desk support to resolve your customers’ or employees’ issues \r\n                                efficiently and on time.                        \r\n                            </p>\r\n                        </div>\r\n                        <button class=\"bg-blue-500 hover:bg-blue-700 text-white font-bold md:ml-4 py-4 px-4 w-full md:w-96 lg:w-10/12 md:text-sm uppercase\">\r\n                            DISCUSS MY HELP DESK NEEDS\r\n                        </button>\r\n                    </div>\r\n                    <h1 class=\"text-2xl md:text-2xl mb-6 font-bold text-gray-800\">\r\n                        Benefits of outsourcing tier 1 help desk\r\n                    </h1>\r\n                    <p class=\"text-md md:text-xl text-gray-600 mb-6\">\r\n                        There are two options to consider when establishing tier 1 help \r\n                        desk: keep it in-house or outsource it. Each one has its benefits in \r\n                        application, depending on your specific situation.<br><br>\r\n                        Establishing <em><strong>in-house tier 1 help desk means</strong></em> your agents will \r\n                        fully know your business specifics, your product/service \r\n                        (in case you set up customer-facing help desk), and work closely \r\n                        with other members of your team. Moreover, you will have full \r\n                        control over in-house agents and their actions. On the downside, building \r\n                        and training a professional help desk team takes time. You’ll need to find \r\n                        experienced agents, onboard them, and ensure their regular training.<br><br>\r\n                        <em><strong>Outsourcing tier 1 help desk</strong></em> eliminates the need to recruit, \r\n                        onboard, and train help desk agents. Outsourced tier 1 help desk can be available \r\n                        24/7, 365 days a year, to handle your employees’ or clients’ urgent issues. \r\n                        Moreover, outsourced tier 1 help desk can reduce the time and investments \r\n                        required for introducing help desk software.\r\n                    </p>\r\n                    <h1 class=\"text-2xl md:text-2xl mb-6 font-bold text-gray-800\">\r\n                        Establish productive tier 1 help desk\r\n                    </h1>\r\n                    <p class=\"text-md md:text-xl text-gray-600 mb-6\">\r\n                        Handling customers’ or employees’ issues quickly and efficiently can \r\n                        be time- and effort-consuming for an in-house team. If you want to skip \r\n                        the burden of help desk support and focus on more critical questions, \r\n                        feel free <a href=\"#\" class=\"text-blue-500 underline\">to reach out to ScienceSoft\'s team</a>.\r\n                    </p>\r\n                    <div class=\"w-full mb-6 p-4 border md:flex\">\r\n                        <div class=\"md:w-3/5 md:mr-6\">\r\n                            <img src=\"https://www.scnsoft.com/_default_upload_bucket/image-thumb__16055__blog_service_snippet/help-desk-outsourcing-services~-~767w.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"mb-4\">\r\n                        </div>\r\n                        <div class=\"md:w-4/5\">\r\n                            <a href=\"#\" class=\"text-blue-500 underline\">\r\n                                <h1 class=\"text-xl hover:text-blue-500 md:text-2xl mb-6 font-bold text-gray-800\">\r\n                                    Help Desk Outsourcing Services by ScienceSoft\r\n                                </h1>\r\n                            </a>\r\n                            <p class=\"text-md md:text-xl text-gray-600 mb-6\">\r\n                                With 12 years in application support, we offer multi-tiered IT support \r\n                                for your enterprise applications or your software products and their users \r\n                                with minimum involvement from your side.\r\n                            </p>\r\n                            <div class=\"flex justify-center md:justify-end lg:justify-end\">\r\n                                <a href=\"#\" class=\"text-blue-500 uppercase\">\r\n                                    Request in support <i class=\"fal fa-arrow-right ml-2\"></i>\r\n                                </a>\r\n                            </div>\r\n                        </div>\r\n                    </div>\r\n                </div>\r\n                <div class=\"lg:w-4/12 hidden lg:block pl-28\">\r\n                    <h1 class=\"text-xl mb-4 font-bold text-gray-800\">\r\n                        Table of contents\r\n                    </h1>\r\n                    <hr class=\"w-12 mb-6 border-b-2 border-yellow-300\">\r\n                    <ul style=\"list-style: square;\" class=\"text-blue-700 m-6\">\r\n                        <a href=\"#\"><li class=\"text-md md:text-lg text-blue-600\">Skills needed for tier 1 help desk agents</li>                        </a>\r\n                        <a href=\"#\"><li class=\"text-md md:text-lg text-blue-600\">Benefits of outsourcing tier 1 help desk</li></a>\r\n                    </ul>\r\n                </div>\r\n            </div>\r\n        </div>\r\n    </body>\r\n</html>', 'https://www.scnsoft.com/', '1613727904.png', NULL, '2021-02-19 04:45:04', '2021-02-19 04:51:24'),
(14, '5246', '24534', '5434', '<!DOCTYPE html>\r\n <html lang=\"en\">\r\n <head>\r\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\r\n    <meta http-equiv=\"X-UA-Compatible\" content=\"IE=edge\">\r\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\r\n    <title>Document</title>\r\n    <link\r\n      href=\"https://unpkg.com/tailwindcss@^2/dist/tailwind.min.css\"\r\n      rel=\"stylesheet\"\r\n    />\r\n </head>\r\n    <body>\r\n\r\n        <div class=\"w-full mb-16 p-4 lg:px-20 md:flex lg:items-center\">\r\n            <div class=\"md:w-2/5 md:mr-6 md:hidden\">\r\n                <img src=\"https://www.brainvire.com/wp/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/auroCRM_banner-1.png\" alt=\"\">\r\n         </div>\r\n          <div class=\"md:w-3/5\">\r\n\r\n             <h1 class=\"text-2xl font-bold mb-4\">360-Degree Auro CRM</h1>\r\n                 <p class=\"text-xl\">Get a clear and concise overview of all your customers in one place    with our 360-degree Auro CRM. Use the neatly organized dashboard in a simple, easy-to-understand manner and get all the information about your customers at your fingertips.\r\n\r\n                </p>\r\n              <a href=\"#\">\r\n                     <button class=\"rounded my-6 py-2 px-4 text-white bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-400     to-blue-500\">\r\n                      <p class=\"\">Learn More</p>\r\n                      </button>            \r\n              </a>\r\n         </div>\r\n           <div class=\"md:w-2/5 md:mr-6 hidden md:block\">\r\n                <img src=\"https://www.brainvire.com/wp/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/auroCRM_banner-1.png\" alt=\"\">\r\n            </div>\r\n         </div>\r\n        <div class=\"w-full md:flex md:items-center  p-4 lg:px-20 bg-gray-200\">\r\n            <div class=\"md:w-1/2 md:mr-6\">\r\n                <h1 class=\"text-2xl font-bold mb-4\">Use Our Customizable Auro CRM</h1>\r\n                <p class=\"text-xl\">Auro CRM is developed keeping in mind all the necessary aspects of a business. It is extremely customizable and forms an extension of your own business rather than an external tool. Auro CRM seamlessly adds to your business and becomes an integral part of it with every bit of features we have designed it to excel in.\r\n                </p>\r\n                <a href=\"#\">\r\n                <button class=\"rounded my-6 py-2 px-4 text-white bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-400 to-blue-500\">\r\n                    <p class=\"\">Contact Us</p>\r\n                </button>            \r\n                </a>\r\n             </div>\r\n              \r\n            <div class=\"md:w-1/2\">\r\n                  <img src=\"https://www.brainvire.com/wp/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/auroCRM_full_use.png\" alt=\"\">\r\n            </div>\r\n       </div>\r\n\r\n   \r\n        <div class=\"w-full mb-16 p-4 lg:px-20 bg-blue-900 p-4\">\r\n        \r\n         <h1 class=\"text-white text-2xl font-bold mb-4\">Multiple Features from One Flexible CRM Solution</h1>\r\n         <p class=\"text-white\">We have specifically designed Auro CRM for complex and multi-faceted setups. It runs diverse features that can boost your business to new heights.</p>\r\n\r\n         <a href=\"#\">\r\n            <button class=\"rounded my-6 py-2 px-4 bg-white hover:text-white hover:bg-blue-800\">\r\n                <p class=\"\">Know More</p>\r\n            </button>            \r\n            </a>\r\n\r\n          \r\n            <div class=\"mt-12 mb-6\">\r\n             <img class =\"w-12 h-12\"src=\"https://www.brainvire.com/wp/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/Multiple-Marketing-Strategies.svg\" alt=\"\">\r\n\r\n\r\n            </div>\r\n            <div>\r\n            <div>\r\n                <h1 class=\"text-2xl font-bold text-white\">Multiple Marketing Strategies</h1>\r\n            </div>\r\n            \r\n            <p class=\"text-white mt-6\">\r\n                Our CRM solution can automate every process while conducting A/B tests and following up over email.\r\n            </p>\r\n            </div>\r\n\r\n\r\n             \r\n             \r\n            <div class=\"mt-12 mb-6\">\r\n                <img class =\"w-12 h-12\"src=\"https://www.brainvire.com/wp/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/Better-Selling-and-Negotiation.svg\" alt=\"\">\r\n   \r\n   \r\n               </div>\r\n               <div>\r\n                   <h1 class=\"text-2xl font-bold text-white\">Better Selling and Negotiation</h1>\r\n               </div>\r\n               <div>\r\n               <p class=\"text-white mt-6\">\r\n                The Auro CRM product is focused on being customer-centric. This enables better negotiation and selling.\r\n               </p>\r\n               </div>\r\n         \r\n\r\n               <div class=\"mt-12 mb-6\">\r\n                <img class =\"w-12 h-12\"src=\"https://www.brainvire.com/wp/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/Deep-Customer-Insights.svg\" alt=\"\">\r\n   \r\n   \r\n               </div>\r\n               <div>\r\n                   <h1 class=\"text-2xl font-bold text-white\">Deep Customer Insights</h1>\r\n               </div>\r\n               <div>\r\n               <p class=\"text-white mt-6\">\r\n                Through our platform, you get a 360-degree view of insights for your business right at your fingertips.\r\n               </p>\r\n               </div>\r\n\r\n               <div class=\"mt-12 mb-6\">\r\n                <img class =\"w-12 h-12\"src=\"https://www.brainvire.com/wp/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/Support-Ticketing-System.svg\" alt=\"\">\r\n   \r\n   \r\n               </div>\r\n               <div>\r\n                   <h1 class=\"text-2xl font-bold text-white\">Support Ticketing System</h1>\r\n               </div>\r\n               <div>\r\n               <p class=\"text-white mt-6\">\r\n                Our dynamic ticketing system can help manage your business better, making communication easy and transparent in the company.\r\n               </p>\r\n               </div>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n               <div class=\"mt-12 mb-6\">\r\n                <img class =\"w-12 h-12\"src=\"https://www.brainvire.com/wp/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/Surveys-Feedbacks.svg\" alt=\"\">\r\n   \r\n   \r\n               </div>\r\n               <div>\r\n                   <h1 class=\"text-2xl font-bold text-white\">Surveys Feedbacks</h1>\r\n               </div>\r\n               <div>\r\n               <p class=\"text-white mt-6\">\r\n                Auro CRM helps you make custom survey forms to get feedback on your products and services from your customers.\r\n               </p>\r\n               </div>\r\n\r\n         \r\n    </body>\r\n</html>', 'jfghjf', NULL, '2021-02-19 07:40:39', '2021-02-19 07:25:14', '2021-02-19 07:40:39');
