(9445, 'en', 'Smart Softwaredelivers one-time services to assess, test and improve the protection level of your network, application or another component of the IT environment. This cooperation model may help you to form an opinion on the vendor and decide whether to cooperate with them afterwards. When getting acquainted with the part of IT environment the customer wants to protect, our security testing team thoroughly studies the details, e.g., gathers and understands the information on software installed on the devices in the network. After that, our security engineers carry out the appropriate cybersecurity services and draw up a report of the achieved results.', 'Smart Softwaredelivers one-time services to assess, test and improve the protection level of your network, application or another component of the IT environment. This cooperation model may help you to form an opinion on the vendor and decide whether to cooperate with them afterwards. When getting acquainted with the part of IT environment the customer wants to protect, our security testing team thoroughly studies the details, e.g., gathers and understands the information on software installed on the devices in the network. After that, our security engineers carry out the appropriate cybersecurity services and draw up a report of the achieved results.', '2021-02-22 08:48:09', '2021-02-22 08:48:09'),
